Description:

****FREE MONOGRAMMED NAME ABOVE DOOR! Just leave me a note when you order with name and color of thread! 
This listing is for TEEPEE COVER ONLY! PLEASE SEE POLE LISTING TO ADD WOOD POLES. WHEN YOU ORDER COVER AND POLES TOGETHER, YOUR TEEPEE WILL COME COMPLETELY ASSEMBLED!
This is my most popular Teepee, very versitle! You can have fun adding your child's personalit to it. It can also be painted. It is made of a medium weight natural color cotton canvas. Pole holders are closed at bottom to prevent poles from scratching floors or slipping out of holders. All seams are professionally finished. The ties, cloth & Velcro & button are made from canvas fabric as well and the buttons are a 1" coconut shell button with tan and brown variations. A loop is placed at the top of door panel section to secure teepee cover from slipping down. 
The 5 pole is a new addition and offers lots of space. All 5 sides are 4ft wide at the bottom. Kids have approximately 66 inches from side to side in all directions for playing space. 5' tall without poles and 62" tall with poles.  Windows can be put on any of the sides. 
The 4 pole Teepee is approximately 4 ft by 4 ft square at bottom and 5' tall without poles and 64" tall with poles.  
The 3 pole teepee is a triangle shape that fits in a corner nicely. The 3 pole has three side that are all approximately 4 ft each and it stands 5 ft tall without poles and 67" tall with poles. 
These teepee are sold with or without poles. If you wish to add your own poles, pole details and assembly instructions are listed below. 
***Custom wood letters on a string are sold seperatly. Can be done in any color!
***Rag fringe is sold separately. 
***Rag fringe and string name attach to cloth loops that are sewn into each side above the door opening. Name and fringe tie through loops.
***window shade are listed seperatly also and come with ties to match door. 
***Pole details:
Pole size no larger than 1 1/4 inch in diameter and 72 to 76 inches long. Home Depot has schedule 40 PVC pipe 1" x  10' and will cut them down to desired length for you, they work perfect and only cost 16. You can use wood or bamboo, it's your choice. A customer said she ordered bamboo poles from Lowes that fit and the cost was around 5 each. 
Teepee assembly:
1: fold out teepee and insert poles, I used a flat head screw driver to help get poles stared in pole holder. 
2: stand teepee and let poles lay on top of one another in a clockwise direction. 
3:tie a decorative string around poles to hold in place. I drilled holes where my poles intersected and taped my sting to a stick and   laced it through poles and tied off  to make it extra secure. A loop is located at the top of the door panel to tie onto to keep cover from sliding down. 
4: decorate as you want and let your lil one have fun.

Product name: Custom Needlepoint Belt
Description:
There is no denying the stylish and elegant nature of a needlepoint belt. As traditional as they are fun, our handmade belts are detailed and of the highest quality. Each needlepoint belt also includes a free monogram to make it even more special. 
The design in the photo is a nautical flag belt, but if you'd prefer a 100% custom design made for you, we'd love to help!  
In your order notes, let us know what you have in mind, including:  
-Belt Size
-Background Color
-Monogram
-Images (you can attach images in an Etsy message, links to them in the notes, if you want us to find something that is also fine)
We will email you a preview for you review and we will adjust as many times as is needed to get it just right.  We don't make any orders until the design has been approved.  It normally takes us 1-4 days to get your preview ready.
Your design is made specific to your belt size, so we email you a preview of your belt to be approved before we make one stitch. It is important that you have the right size on your needlepoint belt, so make sure to read the sizing guide to assure you are getting the size that will fit you.  See the image above to see how to measure.  Be sure to measure to the hole most worn, not necessarily the middle hole.  If you do not have an existing belt to measure, normally 2 - 3 inches larger than the pant size works.
Since we create only the finest quality needlepoint belts, we offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee. For this reason, we ask that you take your time when reviewing and measuring prior to us making the needlepoint belt. Remember that it will take us about 8-12 weeks to stitch and finish your needlepoint belt.
